        <t:profileDesc xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
            <t:creation/>
            <t:abstract>
                <t:p>This record stands for the Life of Lālibalā proper. The text starts by describing the circumstances of his birth, though its central part relates Lālibalā’s ascent to the seventh heaven, where God reveals to him the sanctuaries that were later recreated as the Lālibalā rock-hewn church complex. Having returned to earth, married, undergone a series of tribulations and undertaken a pilgrimage to Jerusalem, Lālibalā is then said to have become a king.</t:p>
            </t:abstract>
